column5: hi all,well went out to cooksbay sunday oct.2.2022 rented boat out off cooksbay marina.first time in a long time we got skunked nada,nothing.not even a follow.we were targetting pike.weather was very windy and very cool.not sure if this had anything to do with not catching anything.but still enjoyed being out on the water.
Hurray! it's high time to remove these restrictions everywhere!
